Name: 589-589 South Western Hwy, Byford
Description: There is a VERY busy one way each way stretch of South West Highway that is pitch dark at night as it has absolutely NO lighting at all, the speed limit is 90km/h, however rarely get to do this as there is so much traffic or slow cars doing 60km/hr. It is double lines due to hills so no overtaking yet I see some people try and it is dangerous! Plus there is often cyclists so it is dangerous to give them the 1metre law. This stretch desperately needs double lanes and street lighting asap.
